subject: Start examples with xwalk-launcher instead of xwalk
commitMessage:
Start examples with xwalk-launcher instead of xwalk

Since the last rebase, the "xwalk" binary of Crosswalk
can not be used to open URLs anymore. Use "xwalk-launcher"
for that instead.

XWALK-2370

Change-Id: I8fe0109a717901d1889cc1e97820c38de190e209
Signed-off-by: Manuel Bachmann <manuel.bachmann@open.eurogiciel.org>
